premise_source_doc_sentence: It was followed in 1990 by the Best Original Art Work award , which was listed again as a special award in 1991 , though not actually awarded , and instated afterward as an official Hugo Award .

The Best Web Site special Hugo award , which was given in 2002 and 2005 , was the latest special award given prior to the Best Series special award , to be given in 2017 in advance of it potentially being ratified as a standard category for the following year .
The next discontinued Hugo award was the Other Forms award , given in 1988 .
A `` fanzine '' is defined for the award as a magazine that does not meet the Hugo award 's criteria for a professional or semi-professional magazine .
The award was originally titled the Hugo Award for Best Non-Fiction Book and was first awarded in 1980 .
